window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Engineer. Survivor. Supervillain.&nbsp;</p> <p>When a down-on-his-luck engineer ends up coming into possession of a rundown suit of power-armor, he sees an opportunity to make some quick cash by selling it off to the nearest supervillain.&nbsp;</p> <p>Unfortunately for him, what should have been a quick and easy sale to pay off his debts quickly grows into an ongoing series of events that serve only to drag him deeper and deeper into the criminal underbelly of the city he calls home.&nbsp;</p> <p>In no time at all, Erich finds himself fending off neo-Nazi gang members, crazed capes, and the dangerous affections of his newest employer's criminally insane daughter.&nbsp;</p> <p>All he wanted to do was make a quick buck . . . .</p>"; 
